import React from 'react' const FullcarsCard = () => { const cars = [ { name: "Creta Hyundai", type: "SUV", discount: "16% Off!", price: "$210", oldPrice: "$250", rating: "4.7 ★", image: "https://via.placeholder.com/150", }, { name: "Innova Crysta", type: "Economy", discount: "10% Off!", price: "$351", oldPrice: "$390", rating: "3.9 ★", image: "https://via.placeholder.com/150", }, { name: "Toyota Etios", type: "Compact", discount: "20% Off!", price: "$192", oldPrice: "$240", rating: "4.5 ★", image: "https://via.placeholder.com/150", }, { name: "Mahindra XUV500", type: "Economy", discount: "15% Off!", price: "$374", oldPrice: "$440", rating: "4.2 ★", image: "https://via.placeholder.com/150", }, ]; return (
{cars.map((car, index) => (

{car.name}

{car.type}
{car.discount}
{car.oldPrice} {car.price}
))}
) } export default FullcarsCard
